Us getting ready for fashion week with @kml.collections 
They are an amazing small business that specializes in tailoring, alterations, customs designs and so much more! It is an amazing group of women, Manuela the designer and owner of @kml.collections it truly an amazing women and it was been such a pleasure working with her for the last few months. It was really an amazing experience getting to follow along with the journey of getting ready for fashion week and then  seeing all the designs hit the main stage @runway7fashion 
And seeing my best friend walking in one of those gorgeous dresses I couldn’t be more filled with excitement and love for @sparklekonplay , you were so gorgeous! ❤️
